ion-of-50-yea/4050-137003/">Green Lantern John Stewart: A Celebration of 50 Years</a> (#87, 182 &amp; 185)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/green-lanterngreen-arrow-space-traveling-heroes/4050-128829/">Green Lantern/Green Arrow: Space Traveling Heroes</a> (#90-106)</li><li><a href="/crisis-on-infinite-earths-companion-deluxe-edition/4000-691351/" data-ref-id="4000-691351">Crisis On Infinite Earths Companion Deluxe Edition Volume 1</a> (#194-198)</li><li><a href="/absolute-green-lanterngreen-arrow/4050-86762/" data-ref-id="4050-86762">Absolute Green Lantern/Green Arrow</a> (#76-87 &amp; 89)</li></ul>', '1960', '205', '{''icon_url'': ''https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/square_avatar/0/4/4457-2013-4869-1-green-lantern.jpg'', ''medium_url'': ''https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/4/4457-2013-4869-1-green-lantern.jpg'', ''screen_url'': ''https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/screen_medium/0/4/4457-2013-4869-1-green-lantern.jpg'', ''screen_large_url'': ''https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/screen_kubrick/0/4/4457-2013-4869-1-green-lantern.jpg'', ''small_url'': ''https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/4/4457-2013-4869-1-green-lantern.jpg'', ''super_url'': ''https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_large/0/4/4457-2013-4869-1-green-lantern.jpg'', ''thumb_url'': ''https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_avatar/0/4/4457-2013-4869-1-green-lantern.jpg'', ''tiny_url'': ''https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/square_mini/0/4/4457-2013-4869-1-green-lantern.jpg'', ''original_url'': ''https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/0/4/4457-2013-4869-1-green-lantern.jpg'', ''image_tags'': ''All Images''}', '[{"id": "Hal Jordan"}, {"id": "Carol Ferris"}, {"id": "Tom Kalmaku"}, {"id": "Green Arrow"}, {"id": "Black Canary"}, {"id": "Katma Tui"}, {"id": "John Stewart"}, {"id": "Carl Ferris"}, {"id": "Bruce Gordon"}, {"id": "Sinestro"}, {"id": "Guy Gardner"}, {"id": "Tomar Re"}, {"id": "Richard Davis"}, {"i