icvine.gamespot.com/coleccionable-marvel-heroes-80-peter-parker-el-esp/4000-612318/">Coleccionable Marvel Héroes - Peter Parker, El Espectacular Spiderman: La Caza de la Araña</a> (#112-130 &amp; #134-136) (Spanish)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/coleccionable-spider-man-6-vida-en-el-pabellon-de-/4000-614363/">Coleccionable Spider-Man - Vida en el pabellón de perros rabiosos</a> (#113) (Spanish)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/100-marvel-hc-spiderman-la-ultima-caceria-de-krave/4050-104357/" data-ref-id="4050-104357">100% Marvel HC. Spiderman: La última cacería de Kraven</a> (#131-132) (Spanish)</li></ul><p>Issues <a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/peter-parker-spiderman/4050-42855/" data-ref-id="4050-42855">#1-63</a> have translated into Spanish.</p>', '1976', '180', '{''icon_url'': ''https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/square_avatar/11/117763/2432028-spectacularspider_man001.jpg'', ''medium_url'': ''https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/11/117763/2432028-spectacularspider_man001.jpg'', ''screen_url'': ''https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/screen_medium/11/117763/2432028-spectacularspider_man001.jpg'', ''screen_large_url'': ''https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/screen_kubrick/11/117763/2432028-spectacularspider_man001.jpg'', ''small_url'': ''https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_small/11/117763/2432028-spectacularspider_man001.jpg'', ''super_url'': ''https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_large/11/117763/2432028-spectacularspider_man001.jpg'', ''thumb_url'': ''https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_avatar/11/117763/2432028-spectacularspider_man001.jpg'', ''tiny_url'': ''https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/square_mini/11/117763/2432028-spectacularspider_man001.jpg'', ''original_url'': ''https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/11/117763/2432028-spectacularspider_man001.jpg'', ''image_tags'': ''All Images''}', '[{"id": "Spider-Man"}, {"id": "Mary Jane"}, {"id": 