de/4050-116977/">Marvel''s Captain Marvel Prelude</a> (#1)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/captain-marvel-starforce/4050-119136/">Captain Marvel: Starforce</a> (#1)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/captain-marvel-the-many-lives-of-carol-danvers/4050-129471/">Captain Marvel: The Many Lives of Carol Danvers</a> (#1 &amp; 19)</li><li><a href="https://comicvine.gamespot.com/guardians-of-the-galaxy-tomorrows-heroes-omnibus/4050-116248/">Guardians of the Galaxy: Tomorrow''s Heroes Omnibus</a> (#23)</li></ul>', '1977', '23', '{''icon_url'': ''https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/square_avatar/0/4/15354-2910-17111-1-ms-marvel.jpg'', ''medium_url'': ''https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/4/15354-2910-17111-1-ms-marvel.jpg'', ''screen_url'': ''https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/screen_medium/0/4/15354-2910-17111-1-ms-marvel.jpg'', ''screen_large_url'': ''https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/screen_kubrick/0/4/15354-2910-17111-1-ms-marvel.jpg'', ''small_url'': ''https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/4/15354-2910-17111-1-ms-marvel.jpg'', ''super_url'': ''https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_large/0/4/15354-2910-17111-1-ms-marvel.jpg'', ''thumb_url'': ''https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/scale_avatar/0/4/15354-2910-17111-1-ms-marvel.jpg'', ''tiny_url'': ''https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/square_mini/0/4/15354-2910-17111-1-ms-marvel.jpg'', ''original_url'': ''https://comicvine.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/0/4/15354-2910-17111-1-ms-marvel.jpg'', ''image_tags'': ''All Images''}', '[{"id": "Carol Danvers"}, {"id": "Dr. Michael Barnett"}, {"id": "J. Jonah Jameson"}, {"id": "Frank Gianelli"}, {"id": "Tracy Burke"}, {"id": "Salia Petrie"}, {"id": "Destructor"}, {"id": "Mystique"}, {"id": "Geoffrey Ballard"}, {"id": "M.O.D.O.K."}, {"id": "Captain Marvel"}, {"id": "Doomsday Man"}, {"id": "Mary Jane"}, {"id": "Yon-Rogg"}, {"id": "Deathbird"}, {"id": "Hecate"}, {"id": "Lynn Andersen"